{"tid":2517650,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"擺脫台灣字體　真正香港字體　同香港人手寫一樣","createTime":"2021-05-05T12:36:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-05T23:21:19.000Z","uid":261647,"like":171,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":63,"replies":[{"pid":"67d34def788640c85338c3f64b1606525bf2a9bb","tid":2517650,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T12:36:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cantonese.tasks/posts/127994539360730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcantonese.tasks%2Fposts%2F127994539360730&d=d89kjzbMxLru5B8Znw6mnwAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=51f15ecd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cantonese.tasks/posts/127994539360730</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmavBidAaKFUGCwNEoTwcGFU4wbWmgWFXT7VU16ipLzYNg?filename=nAv4rhV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnAv4rhV.png&h=daf4be93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n作者：廣東話任務列表<br />\n<br />\n【我只係想幫阿仔印張練字帖，點解隻隻電腦字體都同手寫唔同樣？】<br />\n<br />\n幼稚園派俾小朋友嘅詞語表，啲寫法總係古古怪怪嘅。「雨」字四點要向唔同方向，「户」口個「户」第一劃應該係「丶」，但係有時又打咗做「丿」。呢個問題都好多年，係同電腦字型有關嘅。<br />\n<br />\n只要你屋企部機係用台灣字型，啲寫法就同日常正常寫法唔同。〖圖一〗用六隻字Mac機字型，你睇下，你用邊一款都總會有啲事。有時你打香港嘅字（好似衞生個衞）仲要缺咗字添。用 Windows 嘅朋友，新細明體、標楷體都係隻隻字體都有啲唔同。下面咁多隻字體，得楷書係真正貼近手寫字。但係抄寫嚟講，初學寫字都冇乜幾何會用毛筆啦，基本上都係硬筆，用明體、用楷體，都唔啱硬筆書法。如果我想整返啲硬筆嘅字帖俾小朋友温書，要點？將就下囉，簡體字就有，你用唔用？定係要用娃娃體？<br />\n<br />\n所以我好想有〖圖2〗呢種手寫體嘅練字帖同埋電腦字型。起碼係第一，個筆劃可以跟返香港主流習慣（而唔係台灣標準、中國大陸標準，亦都唔會跟足教育局嗰個字表）；第二，個字型係似硬筆書法，唔好係美術字，等學生可以掌握返個筆順。<br />\n<br />\n而家 cjkFonts 搞緊呢個眾籌，得返幾日時間，想大家幫手。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cjkfonts.io/campaign/futurefont\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cjkfonts.io%2Fcampaign%2Ffuturefont&d=d89kjzbMxLru5B8Znw6mnwAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=52eeea8d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cjkfonts.io/campaign/futurefont</a><br />\n<br />\n整中文字體係苦差嚟，冇乜人肯做。大家有錢出錢有力出力。希望下年今日，中文科、常識科嘅老師唔使再苦惱字體問題，家長温書嗰陣有隻工整嘅手寫字體可以用。"},{"pid":"eee0a191cf0a4a5256da0915e75594fa8d4e189f","tid":2517650,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T13:41:33.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"801858d066194957180974f3a30b82fe92fd0c65","tid":2517650,"uid":275912,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T14:01:50.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n有啲學校仲話正常字體錯<br />\n要跟電腦字ON99"},{"pid":"f14c4949b44db235c8669777e3cc4d8117e27f72","tid":2517650,"uid":24123,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T14:03:04.000Z","msg":"認真野要推"},{"pid":"491203fe81f9b0937b22372ed792525d7d5dfd43","tid":2517650,"uid":223428,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T14:03:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ee0c3b48d44159d27486f4b34547ec8145bf36b","tid":2517650,"uid":67816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T14:04:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"44859efdfebc2e0b4a4c42ff7a1b05c0f03084e6","tid":2517650,"uid":64874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T14:06:06.000Z","msg":"上個期我用早鳥價支持佢地，當然佢地第一水係$560，我唔夠早所以無參加<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/door.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23ff7fcbdd70233bd7da8f027f08574fb13c0a9b","tid":2517650,"uid":43178,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T14:07:27.000Z","msg":"Apple 出咗隻字體有香港版，叫蘋方-香港<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmeWkpAokzo7fABhg7u9owEeyq2oscvTJZEspsN9ocJpP1?filename=XkfW2w5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXkfW2w5.png&h=7648acdf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b6b4f8039c0c9dcd214156095488c2f8c1a15f02","tid":2517650,"uid":11663,"like":7,"dislike":10,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"23ff7fcbdd70233bd7da8f027f08574fb13c0a9b","tid":2517650,"uid":43178,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T14:07:27.000Z","msg":"Apple 出咗隻字體有香港版，叫蘋方-香港<br />