.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.edbchinese.hk%2Flexlist_en%2F&d=d89kjzbMxLru5B8Znw6mnwAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=014f96d7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.edbchinese.hk/lexlist_en/</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T15:07:00.000Z","msg":"香港根本無一套法定標準字形<br />\n《常用字字形表》只係作參考，唔係一鎚定音係得果種寫法"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T15:20:14.000Z","msg":"我只係覺得上面D人好好笑，面紅耳赤咁爭論<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所謂「真正香港字體」究竟係點定<br />\n大家唔係香港人咩？點解幾隻字已經要爭論咁耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/crowd.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/crowd.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48893255bdf2386671e6f69a22775ba8ec4dcbc5","tid":2517650,"uid":173207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67d34def788640c85338c3f64b1606525bf2a9bb","tid":2517650,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T12:36:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cantonese.tasks/posts/127994539360730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcantonese.tasks%2Fposts%2F127994539360730&d=d89kjzbMxLru5B8Znw6mnwAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=51f15ecd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cantonese.tasks/posts/127994539360730</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nAv4rhV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnAv4rhV.png&h=daf4be93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n作者：廣東話任務列表<br />\n<br />\n【我只係想幫阿仔印張練字帖，點解隻隻電腦字體都同手寫唔同樣？】<br />\n<br />\n幼稚園派俾小朋友嘅詞語表，啲寫法總係古古怪怪嘅。「雨」字四點要向唔同方向，「户」口個「户」第一劃應該係「丶」，但係有時又打咗做「丿」。呢個問題都好多年，係同電腦字型有關嘅。<br />\n<br />\n只要你屋企部機係用台灣字型，啲寫法就同日常正常寫法唔同。〖圖一〗用六隻字Mac機字型，你睇下，你用邊一款都總會有啲事。有時你打香港嘅字（好似衞生個衞）仲要缺咗字添。用 Windows 嘅朋友，新細明體、標楷體都係隻隻字體都有啲唔同。下面咁多隻字體，得楷書係真正貼近手寫字。但係抄寫嚟講，初學寫字都冇乜幾何會用毛筆啦，基本上都係硬筆，用明體、用楷體，都唔啱硬筆書法。如果我想整返啲硬筆嘅字帖俾小朋友温書，要點？將就下囉，簡體字就有，你用唔用？定係要用娃娃體？<br />\n<br />\n所以我好想有〖圖2〗呢種手寫體嘅練字帖同埋電腦字型。起碼係第一，個筆劃可以跟返香港主流習慣（而唔係台灣標準、中國大陸標準，亦都唔會跟足教育局嗰個字表）；第二，個字型係似硬筆書法，唔好係美術字，等學生可以掌握返個筆順。<br />\n<br />\n而家 cjkFonts 搞緊呢個眾籌，得返幾日時間，想大家幫手。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cjkfonts.io/campaign/futurefont\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cjkfonts.io%2Fcampaign%2Ffuturefont&d=d89kjzbMxLru5B8Znw6mnwAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=52eeea8d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cjkfonts.io/campaign/futurefont</a><br />\n<br />\n整中文字體係苦差嚟，冇乜人肯做。大家有錢出錢有力出力。希望下年今日，中文科、常識科嘅老師唔使再苦惱字體問題，家長温書嗰陣有隻工整嘅手寫字體可以用。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T15:20:44.000Z","msg":"我記得小學ETV有教台灣同香港字體唔同"},{"pid":"91142b66c5d3e0bf845d0b69d694b69ddce9bb46","tid":2517650,"uid":7708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"20dd14733cc671637debc92fa53e31c738fb5dd4","tid":2517650,"uid":170399,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a4ce54b46d35339b231ba3275a7590bcc92155d3","tid":2517650,"uid":7708,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d230b94927d2c4eff99a60ff4e7c0b425708ad4","tid":2517650,"uid":170399,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T15:00:02.000Z","msg":"我就唔係好知大家所講「香港字體」既意思係乜<br />\n<br />\n如果係想講小學學果D，不如大家查下先，免得口同鼻拗<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.edbchinese.hk/lexlist_en/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.edbchinese.hk%2Flexlist_en%2F&d=d89kjzbMxLru5B8Znw6mnwAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=014f96d7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.edbchinese.hk/lexlist_en/</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T15:07:00.000Z","msg":"香港根本無一套法定標準字形<br />\n《常用字字形表》只係作參考，唔係一鎚定音係得果種寫法"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T15:20:14.000Z","msg":"我只係覺得上面D人好好笑，面紅耳赤咁爭論<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所謂「真正香港字體」究竟係點定<br />\n大家唔係香港人咩？點解幾隻字已經要爭論咁耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/crowd.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/crowd.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T15:25:59.000Z","msg":"真係得啖笑&hellip;唔知佢地用咩準則去爭論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abdd8477fc37876edd8f9c7d5ebd312f31842910","t